data.description: GIGANTIC PRICE IMPROVEMENT! Down $70,000.00 from original list price. Waterfront. What are you waiting for? Just try to find this anywhere at this price! 4 bedroom, 2-bathroom home, 2 car garage and huge pool on the water to Lake Pierce with covered boat dock. Updated over head water piping. Updated AC w/new duct vents. Updated drain field. Resurfaced pool w/updated pool pump. 2 Tri sliding glass doors open to pool for an awesome view. Updated seawall. Crown molding throughout most of the house. Central vacuum system.  36" granite vanities in both bathrooms. Both bathroom doors lead out to pool deck. This home sits on .35 acres. Come fish Lake Pierce, which is over 3700 acres. Your view from your pool overlooks the water, deck and boathouse.  Enjoy your evenings by the firepit after a long day of fishing! Not to mention a real Fireplace in the family room for those somewhat chilly nights! Lanai that also overlooks a vaulted screened pool. Minutes to town. This home is on cul-de-sac. Centrally located between both east and west coast beaches. Well known Bok Tower and Cherry Pocket Lakefront Restaurant just a few miles away. --Close to major attractions in Orlando as well as Lego Land in Winter Haven. I bet your family would love for you to own this amazing Florida Home! Call me to see.
